{"tid":1787969,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被告9月一日持刀追擊示威者後 今向法官稱警察說沒有需要自首","createTime":"2019-12-18T09:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T10:20:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1d9ad9bf9a7b16448fae772634cfa8c297fd3195","tid":1787969,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:57:47.000Z","msg":"網民早前發起「901機場見」活動，圖堵塞交通並妨礙機場運作，及後爆發警民衝突，大批示威者徒步離開機場前往東涌。當日下午，有地盤工在東涌逸東邨附近持刀作勢追斬示威者及街坊，市民爭相走避，有市民拍下事發片段。地盤工今在西九龍裁判法院承認在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求情稱持刀只是為嚇人，更謂事後已問警方需否自首，警方卻回應暫沒有需要。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n被告蔡彼得（45歲）早前否認控罪，案件原定今預審，惟被告改口認罪。裁判官劉綺雲押後案件至明年1月8日，待索閱被告的背景報告及翻看涉案片段後始判刑，其間被告須還柙。劉官明言，會考慮判處被告坐監。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191218/60391218?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F60391218%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BunT1AxqF%2FibzLHEE6598sd0%3D&h=c8c677f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191218%2F60391218%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6f5bee5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191218/60391218?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"619d1c83f9d513231dfd24ae37889d5ede4fbc32","tid":1787969,"uid":133033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:01:17.000Z","msg":"持刀傷人都係考慮坐監咋？"},{"pid":"2dd5149e3262be548d27b78f6e71035a26a619f9","tid":1787969,"ui